description:
Falling for a Dancer is based on Deirdre Purcell's much beloved novel, and with Colin Farrell, Elisabeth Dermot Walsh and Liam Cunningham on board you really can't go wrong. A woman is forced into an arranged marriage after becoming pregnant during a meaningless fling, but her frustration at living in the company of her brutish husband in an isolated Cork village provokes a flirtatious encounter with young Daniel McCarthy in full view of the entire village; an episode she soon comes to regret.
